data.name: ReadFips1
data.value: select top(1) [STATE], COUNTY, LOCATION, COUNTY_DESC, STATE_ABBREVIATION, COUNTY_ABBR from CKT_FIPS where (STATE_ABBREVIATION = @stateAbbreviation) and (COUNTY_ABBR = @countyAbbr)

data.name: ReadFips2
data.value: select top(1) [STATE], COUNTY, LOCATION, COUNTY_DESC, STATE_ABBREVIATION, COUNTY_ABBR from CKT_FIPS where STATE_ABBREVIATION = @stateAbbreviation
